&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Core design principles:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>YOLO Rust Deployment Guide</title><link>/en/posts/aihelper/yolo-rust-deployment/</link><pubDate>Fri, 29 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>/en/posts/aihelper/yolo-rust-deployment/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="chapter-9-complete-yolo-tutorial-with-rust"&gt;Chapter 9: Complete YOLO Tutorial with Rust&lt;/h2&gt;
